name: Kohe 10
description: You are aboard Alfa Romero Model 626-300 Spaceship Emperor bound for a star in Sagiterius. You are traveling with innocent people and your mission is to hijack the spaceship since you are a hijacker hiding in the back room. Unfortenlily the passengers have other tricks up their sleeves as they try to beat you back from reaching cockpit. Security droids discuised as Kokoka balls try to set u back.
